      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled CFD solver with documented release notes and regression test suite; MRL 2 requires Gradation 1 compliance.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional software QA protocol. Version control logs, release notes, and a regression test suite covering rotating machinery cases are on file. Gradation 1 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
